### API Node.js TypeScript Example - HTTP Requests

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/health

### Root endpoint
GET http://localhost:3000/

### Register User
POST http://localhost:3000/api/users/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Junior",
  "email": "micorreojunior@gmail.com",
  "password": "123456",
  "role": "USER"
}

